DESCRIPTION:

 cfglib is a library of two common library,usualy using in configure or 
 settings of software.
 The first one is 'section',the form is like this:
  [header1]
  tag1=value1
  tag2=value2
  [header2]
  tag1=value1
  tag2=value5
 The second one is 'xml',this is an well-known text formatting,you may 
 know this already.
  <tag1>something<tag2>
 ***This library is tiny tool for parsing 'section' or 'xml' -file,it'll 
 ***not support some complex operations.

